metadata.name: Be fire, my friend
metadata.description:
I chose this photo because it is bright, it is alive, it is playful and a little dangerous.  That’s how I see the element of fire and in my life this is an integral element that moves me, saturates, revives and, of course burns.

Title: "Be fire, my friend"

Artist: Kohakugava
